<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Linux on Hsing-Yu Shih</title><link>https://www.hugoshih.com/tags/linux/</link><description>Recent content in Linux on Hsing-Yu Shih</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 20:56:58 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.hugoshih.com/tags/linux/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Build U-boot for QEMU</title><link>https://www.hugoshih.com/p/build-u-boot-for-qemu/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 20:56:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.hugoshih.com/p/build-u-boot-for-qemu/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://i.imgur.com/mzEAvua.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Build U-boot for QEMU" />&lt;h4 id="install-dependencies">Install Dependencies
&lt;/h4>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
